ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectCertain Fees Relating to Export Certificates Remission Order
PrecisExport Certificates Remission Order, which grants remission of the portion of the fee that exceeds $75.00 paid or payable for the issuance of an export certificate for live animals or embryos during the period beginning on October 1, 2009 and ending on September 30, 2011, if an accredited veterinarian provided the inspection services on which the export certificate is based, for an amount estimated at $4,011,378.
